{"tid":898903,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"未補地價居屋點還債？","createTime":"2018-11-12T04:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T05:51:54.000Z","uid":47360,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c96aa6b119ce7d9caf6a7cec07e39eec3e8be881","tid":898903,"uid":47360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:24:04.000Z","msg":"如果你欠人週身債，但有間未補地價居屋，究竟有咩方法幫到自己？<br />\n<br />\ntg 我傾下（非財仔/銀行）<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/litsoldier\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flitsoldier&d=Jjls0yldg%2BbC47GMtSCu9zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=4dddacbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/litsoldier</a><br />\n<br />\n經驗分享"},{"pid":"7b327273d9fbfb65d01bb6c79dc19d7edfe148a6","tid":898903,"uid":40397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:25:10.000Z","msg":"如果係正常野咪係度講"},{"pid":"dbe62c16c12fa730b6e896641a9bc476ba9402cc","tid":898903,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c96aa6b119ce7d9caf6a7cec07e39eec3e8be881","tid":898903,"uid":47360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:24:04.000Z","msg":"如果你欠人週身債，但有間未補地價居屋，究竟有咩方法幫到自己？<br />\n<br />\ntg 我傾下（非財仔/銀行）<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/litsoldier\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flitsoldier&d=Jjls0yldg%2BbC47GMtSCu9zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=4dddacbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/litsoldier</a><br />\n<br />\n經驗分享"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:26:17.000Z","msg":"賣左佢"},{"pid":"489f845f1e6c07e1c3fd953c2bc97e09770413b6","tid":898903,"uid":143940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:37:31.000Z","msg":"未補價居屋可加按套現？<br />\n居屋近年貴過私樓，很多市民問未補地價居屋能否加按或翻按套現，雖然筆者是按揭財技專家，但業主若非遇上生死大事，套現近乎沒有可能。<br />\n未補地價居屋或公屋戶想套現，需向房署申請，而房署只會因應一些人生難關才批准，例如醫藥費、財困、白事、贍養費等，而且套現金額只限所需範圍，例如疾病手術費10萬元，房署就只准套現10萬元。<br />\n至於財困，業主需證明欠財務公司債務，入息不足以支付利息，房署才會考慮批准居屋業主套現解困。有人問：「我可唔可以寫張借據畀屋企人，然後用財困呢個理由申請加按套現？」答案是不能。據筆者理解，財困要牽涉欠高利貸級數的困境。信用卡數大部分情況下都能以入息支付最低還款額，不算是財困。<br />\n房署批准後，銀行才可以承造按揭，利息不是一般最優惠利率(P)減3%，而是根據個別情況批核，例如貸款人的TU和入息，筆者見過最高為P+1.5%，即實際利率達6.5厘以上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metrodaily.hk/metro_columns/未補價居屋可加按套現？/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fmetro_columns%2F%E6%9C%AA%E8%A3%9C%E5%83%B9%E5%B1%85%E5%B1%8B%E5%8F%AF%E5%8A%A0%E6%8C%89%E5%A5%97%E7%8F%BE%EF%BC%9F%2F&d=Jjls0yldg%2BbC47GMtSCu9zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=004b0fa4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metrodaily.hk/metro_columns/未補價居屋可加按套現？/</a>"},{"pid":"37073517be6059735ecd3f896c3e3e7e2a5a200e","tid":898903,"uid":16685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:04:00.000Z","msg":"都冇問題"},{"pid":"6f278f4e620844fdfcc6f0f19b29ad3a9afd1443","tid":898903,"uid":18395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"咪俾錢中介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}